abstract: Cisco will buy Starent Networks, which makes products that help wireless telecommunications companies ship large volumes of data to phones and computing devices.
snippet: Cisco will buy Starent Networks, which makes products that help wireless telecommunications companies ship large volumes of data to phones and computing devices.
lead_paragraph: Another week, another $3 billion acquisition for Cisco Systems.

headline.main: In Latest Deal, Cisco Buys Starent for $2.9 Billion
